{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be lively and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Azure Bistro</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #0077cc; /* Brand Blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand Blue */\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .menu-items, .locations {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .menu-item, .location-card {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin: 15px;\n            width: 30%;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .menu-item:hover, .location-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .menu-item h3, .location-card h3 {\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand Blue */\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        .menu-item p, .location-card p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #0077cc; /* Brand Blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #005fa3; /* Darker Blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .menu-item, .location-card {\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Azure Bistro</h1>\n        <p>Experience the Taste of Excellence</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section>\n            <h2>Our Signature Dishes</h2>\n            <div class=\"menu-items\">\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Oceanic Pasta</h3>\n                    <p>Fresh seafood tossed with linguine in a light lemon-garlic sauce.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Azure Burger</h3>\n                    <p>Our classic beef burger topped with blue cheese and caramelized onions.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Skyline Salad</h3>\n                    <p>Mixed greens, grilled chicken, avocado, and a vibrant blueberry vinaigrette.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#locations\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Full Menu</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"locations\">\n            <h2>Our Locations</h2>\n            <div class=\"locations\">\n                <div class=\"location-card\">\n                    <h3>Downtown</h3>\n                    <p>123 Main Street, Metropolis</p>\n                    <p>Open Daily: 11 AM - 10 PM</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"location-card\">\n                    <h3>Uptown</h3>\n                    <p>456 Oak Avenue, Metropolis</p>\n                    <p>Open Daily: 11 AM - 10 PM</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"location-card\">\n                    <h3>Seaside</h3>\n                    <p>789 Ocean Drive, Metropolis</p>\n                    <p>Open Daily: 11 AM - 10 PM</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Make a Reservation</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Azure Bistro. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}